License summary
===============

This software contains source files under a variety of different open source
licenses.  Currently, some of the source files (notably, Xapian) are
distributed under the terms of the GPL (version 2 or later).  Other source
files (ie, the MongoDB driver) are distributed under the terms of the Apache 2
License, which is compatible with the GPL version 3.  As a result, when
distributing the package as a whole, the terms of the GPL version 3 must be
followed.  However individual files and components are released under less
restrictive licenses than the GPL.

