This file contains fragments copied from the Xapian core source code, licensed under
the GPL, version 2 or later.

Xapian
======

The following files are copied from the Xapian source tree.  These files are
licensed under the GPL, version 2 (or later at your discretion).  See the
individual files for details of the copyright holders.

 - m4/xapian.m4
 - libs/xapiancommon/

